{
    "version": "1.2",
    "description": "PyGlimmer - Python逆向工程集成工具，支持PyInstaller/Pyarmor解包及pyc反编译",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/yoruak1/PyGlimmer",
    "license": "GPL-3.0-only",
    "url": "https://github.com/yoruak1/PyGlimmer/archive/refs/tags/v1.2.zip#/pyglimmer.zip",
    "hash": "sha256:a9138fa6d6a2f1eb9f4d6402cc3dfdde53899666a7ab280d28c31ca90d40b4f3",
    "extract_dir": "PyGlimmer-1.2",
    "suggest": {
        "python": "python"
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\pyglimmer.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0', '@python PyGlimmer.py %*', '@popd' -Encoding Ascii"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "pip install -r \"$dir\\requirements.txt\" --quiet"
    ],
    "bin": "pyglimmer.bat",
    "checkver": {
        "url": "https://github.com/yoruak1/PyGlimmer/releases",
        "regex": "PyGlimmer v([\\d.]+)"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "url": "https://github.com/yoruak1/PyGlimmer/archive/refs/tags/v$version.zip#/pyglimmer.zip",
        "extract_dir": "PyGlimmer-$version"
    },
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: 安全测试/逆向工程",
        "【主要功能】: PyInstaller/Pyarmor解包、pyc字节码反编译、加密字节码解密",
        "【适用场景】: Python程序逆向分析、安全审计",
        "【技术特点】: 基于Python 3.8+，支持uncompyle6、decompyle3、pycdc等多引擎",
        "【注意事项】: 首次运行会自动安装依赖，PyLingual需自行安装并配置环境变量"
    ]
}
